Package: SeuratBayesian
Title: Bayesian Differential Expression for Seurat via ZINB Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alexander Sadler
Maintainer: Alexander Sadler <alexander@apexomic.com>
Description: Provides zero-inflated negative bionomial (ZINB) Bayesian
  modelling for single-cell RNA-seq data stored as Seurat objects.
